name: ali jordan

portfolio.name: 2 bedroom painting
portfolio.description: Moonlight dripped through ancient oaks, weaving shadows on moss-covered stones. A lone owl hooted, its cry echoing through the stillness. A fox rustled in the undergrowth, its eyes gleaming emeralds in the darkness.
